TradeChina is an O2O foreign trade service platform for international exhibitions organized by Meorient business exhibition co., Ltd, which provides sourcing, searching, inquiry, and transaction services for international buyers and Chinese suppliers. It also provides Chat, Translation, Meeting and other value-added services, the core purpose is making the exhibition show as the starting point, to promote the match rate between international buyers and China suppliers of trade.
The platform during the exhibition focused on exhibitors and buyers to provide a full range of supporting services, in the non-exhibition period for buyers to provide online quick sourcing, matching, inquiry services, and follow-up trade links extension services.
First, the platform serve for the Belt and Road countries by the HOMELIFE EXHIBITION shows:
1, China (Turkey) Trade Fair - Eurasian Istanbul - Istanbul World Trade Center;
2, China (Poland) Trade Fair - Central and Eastern Europe Poland Warsaw - Warsaw International Exhibition Center;
3, China (Mexico) Trade Fair - Mexico City, Mexico City - Mexico City Convention and Exhibition Center;
4, China (Egypt) Trade Fair - North Africa Egypt Cairo - Cairo International Exhibition Center;
5, China (South Africa) Trade Fair - South Africa Johannesburg - Thornton Conference Center;
6, China (Jordan) Trade Fair - Middle East Jordan Amman - Amman International Exhibition Center;
7, China (Brazil) Trade Fair - South America Brazil Sao Paulo - Pan American International Exhibition Center;
8, China (Kazakhstan) Trade Fair - Central Asia Kazakhstan Almaty - Adakent Exhibition Center;
9, China (India) Trade Fair - South Asia India Mumbai - Mumbai International Exhibition Center;
10, China (UAE) Trade Fair - Middle East United Arab Emirates Dubai - Dubai International Exhibition Center;
